We used Dell Optiplex 9020 machine with intel i7 processor, 16 GB RAM and Ubuntu 16.04 operating system.


To run the simulation:
1) Make sure SUMO is installed on your computer. Installation procedure for different Operating Systems is provided at http://sumo.sourceforge.net/userdoc/Downloads.html
1) Set the path to sumo folder as environment variable:
	for example in linux, 
    export SUMO_HOME=/usr/share/sumo

2) run the python script 'run.py' using the following command
	python3 run.py

3) In the sumo gui window that opens, set the delay to maximum (1000) and wait for the output on the terminal.